title: D5 Sup/Jng/Mid LF Ranked Team
body: Add me in game or comment down below if you want me

replies.body: I am not sure if you have read my post, but my team is looking for a jungler main for a ranked team to compete in the open ladder tournaments. I'm not sure whether you're looking for a serious team with scheduled practices etc but we'd love to have you IF your motivated enough :)
